==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Repleader
<hw>Re*plead"er</hw> <pr>(-?r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Law)</fld>
<def>A second pleading, or course of pleadings; also, the right of
pleading again.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Whenever a <qex>repleader</qex> is granted, the pleadings must
begin <qex>de novo</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Blackstone.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Replenish</ent>⟦br⟧
